nodes.text: Winama Naberrie was a Human female who was the mother of Ruwee Naberrie, the grandmother of Padmé Amidala, and the great-grandmother of Luke Skywalker and Leia Organa Solo. Winama was known as one of Theed's best cloth weavers. In 33 BBY, she passed away when Padmé was elected Monarch of Naboo. Padmé described her as a humorous woman who gave her the feeling that she could have done anything.
